By Sampson Unamka Ex-BBNaija stars, Khafi, Ike, Venita alongside TV Host Nancy Isime , Simi Drey, singer, Praiz and one of Africa’s funniest men, Basketmouth in one tv commercial! That’s a whole lot of your favourite celebrities and beautiful people in one ad, right? That’s the list of stars in the new television commercial by MultiChoice to launch 5 new DStv and GOtv packages.
The commercial is titled ‘Happier Holidays with DStv’ and demonstrates the happiness and ‘feels’ that come with a typical festive season in Nigeria.